<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Breast Cancer Detection</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .hero-section {
      height: 100vh;
      background: url('your-background-image.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .hero-section p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .btn-custom {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .feature-card img {
      border-top-left-radius: 10px;
      border-top-right-radius: 10px;
    }
    .feature-card-body {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-card h5 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #6c757d;
    }
    section#features {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .return {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        background-color: #007bff;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .return:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    
    .return:focus {
        outline: none;
    }
    
    .return-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh; /* Centers the button vertically */
    }
    
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4">AI-Powered Early Detection</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-4">Innovative AI technologies are revolutionizing breast cancer detection by analyzing medical images more accurately and faster than traditional methods. This allows for earlier diagnosis and more effective treatments, potentially saving lives.</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card feature-card">
            <img src="images/momo graphy.png" class="card-img-top" alt="AI in Mammography" height="200" width="100">
            <div class="card-body feature-card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">AI-Assisted Mammograms</h5>
              <p class="card-text">AI tools assist in reading mammogram images, identifying early signs of breast cancer, which might be overlooked by human eyes. These systems help radiologists make more accurate assessments.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card feature-card">
            <img src="images/ultra sound tech.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Ultrasound Technology" height="200" width="100">
            <div class="card-body feature-card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Advanced Ultrasound Technology</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Breast ultrasound, coupled with AI analysis, helps detect abnormalities in the tissue, especially in women with dense breast tissue. AI enhances the interpretation of ultrasound results, increasing diagnostic accuracy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card feature-card">
            <img src="images/watch-this-handheld-device-can-detect-breast-tumours-as-small-as-3-5-mm.webp" class="card-img-top" alt="Mobile Screening" height="200" width="100">
            <div class="card-body feature-card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Mobile Screening Devices</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Mobile breast cancer screening devices equipped with AI technology are making breast cancer detection more accessible, particularly in rural and underserved areas, allowing women to screen at home.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="return" href="/">Back Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
